---+!! %TOPIC%

Currently UKP Lab maintains the computational resources listed belwow on its own. There are additional ressources that can be used from TU Darmstadts "[[https://www.hrz.tu-darmstadt.de/hlr/hochleistungsrechnen/index.de.jsp][Lichtenberg HLR]]" and the Hessian AI Cluster "[[https://hessian.ai/supercomputer-for-cutting-edge-ai-research-in-hesse/][fourtytwo]]". 

---++ Overview Compute Cluster
   * 13 nodes
   * ~ 2400 CPU Cores
   * ~ 14,5 TB memory
   * ~ 0,75 PB central storage capacity
   * 36x GPUs with >= 80GB VRAM
      * NVIDIA A100 (80GB) 32x
      * NVIDIA H100 (80GB): 4x
   * 45x GPUs with < 80GB VRAM
      * NVIDIA P100 (16GB): 2x
      * NVIDIA TITAN RTX (24GB): 3x
      * NVIDIA V100 (32GB): 8x
      * NVIDIA A100 (40GB): 8x
      * NVIDIA L40 (45GB): 8
      * NVIDIA RTX A6000 (48GB): 8

---++ Overview LLM CLuster
   * 4 nodes
   * ~ 400 CPU Cores
   * ~ 4TB MEMORY
   * ~ 250 TB central storage capacity
   * 13x GPUs with < 80GB VRAM
      * NVIDIA P100 (16GB): 5x
      * NVIDIA L40s (45GB): 8x

---++ Summary
   * 17 nodes
   * ~ 2800 CPU cores
   * ~ 18,5 TB memory
   * 94 GPUs

